flow-state|creative_movement_physical_rhythm_deep_focus_social_exchange|concentrated|creative_movement|physical_rhythm|deep_focus|social_exchange|Ideas with movement behind them|You are most likely to find flow when ideas can move and the body, pace, or setting helps keep them alive.|This pattern often shows up when a fresh angle appears through action, walking, making, changing location, or shifting pace. Physical Rhythm helps Creative Movement avoid becoming too crowded in the head. Deep Focus gives the best idea enough substance once it is worth developing. Social Exchange becomes useful when the result needs testing with another person.|active|flow-state::creative_movement_physical_rhythm_deep_focus_social_exchange::concentrated
