flow-state|social_exchange_physical_rhythm_creative_movement_deep_focus|balanced|social_exchange|physical_rhythm|creative_movement|deep_focus|Flexible flow through contact and pace|You may find flow through exchange, movement, ideas, or focus depending on the work in front of you.|Social Exchange appears first, but the ranking should be treated lightly. Some tasks may need another person. Some may need movement or a fresh angle. Some may need quiet concentration before they are complete. The useful move is to choose the condition that turns live momentum into clear progress.|active|flow-state::social_exchange_physical_rhythm_creative_movement_deep_focus::balanced
